<li><a href="http://www.gmu.edu/departments/economics/bcaplan/e410/econ410.htm" class="external text" title="http://www.gmu.edu/departments/economics/bcaplan/e410/econ410.htm" rel="nofollow">Notes for a course in public choice</a> by Bryan Caplan</li>
<li><a href="http://perspicuity.net/sd/pub-choice.html" class="external text" title="http://perspicuity.net/sd/pub-choice.html" rel="nofollow">Introduction to Public Choice Theory</a> by Leon Felkins. Contains numerous links of interest</li>
<li><a href="http://www.nomadpress.com/public_choice/34432.html" class="external text" title="http://www.nomadpress.com/public_choice/34432.html" rel="nofollow">The Field of Public Choice</a> by Pat Gunning</li>
<li><a href="http://www.pubchoicesoc.org/about2.htm" class="external text" title="http://www.pubchoicesoc.org/about2.htm" rel="nofollow">"Statement of Purpose,"</a> Public Choice Society</li>
<li><a href="http://www.canaktan.org/ekonomi/anayasal_iktisat/anasayfa-anayasaliktisat.htm" class="external text" title="http://www.canaktan.org/ekonomi/anayasal_iktisat/anasayfa-anayasaliktisat.htm" rel="nofollow">Turkish Public Choice Site</a></li>
<li><a href="http://unjobs.org/tags/public-choice-theory" class="external text" title="http://unjobs.org/tags/public-choice-theory" rel="nofollow">Public choice documents on unjobs.org</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.constitution.org/pd/pd.htm" class="external text" title="http://www.constitution.org/pd/pd.htm" rel="nofollow">Prisoners' Dilemma and Public Choice Theory</a></li>
</ul>


